Build and install instructions for Notmuchfs.

Compilation commands
--------------------
Simply:
 $ make

Platforms
---------
Any platform that supports FUSE and Notmuch should be supported, but only
64-bit Arch-linux has been tested extensively.

Dependencies
------------

  Notmuch
  -------
  Tested with 0.13.

  FUSE
  ----
  Required >= 2.6, tested with 2.8.7.
